descriptionHtml:
Feel the game of basketball with Block’em All! Protect the rim by blocking shots! Go for slam dunks! Win the matches! Play the tournaments and earn the cups!

Block the shots and go for slam dunks
Show your basketball skills, challenge the shots,steal the balls, block the dunk attempts , defend the rim and win the matches! On offense, go for crazy moves, alley-oops, dunks! Posterize your opponents!

Build your own player
Unlock the players, unlockt the amazing snekaers, collect keys to get sleeves, hats bags and balls! The more levels you completed, the more items you will get to build your player! Become an all star!

Improve your career
Play more to advance in your career! Become rookie of the year, be in the defensive team of the year, then defensive player of the league and most valuable player of the league! M.V.P! M.V.P!

Game features:
Different basketball courts
Alley-oop, shoot around, boss and ball machine levels
Fever mode to become bigger and taller
Dunk levels
Upgradable cheerleaders and fans
30+ player characters
20+ sneakers
100+ customisations items
Free to play!
